Name:		%{sname}_%{pgmajorversion}
Version:	1.0
Release:	1PIGSTY%{?dist}
Summary:	Output plugin for logical replication in Raw SQL format
License:	PostgreSQL
URL:		https://github.com/michaelpq/pg_plugins/blob/main/decoder_raw/
